{"type": "article", "id": 39078, "title": "你见过这种随波逐流的超薄花瓶吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-22T23:17:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 38800, "name": "田中达也"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 213, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170322214207T0BY7Autjcx28O5Z.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Jellyfish Vase by nendo</h3><p>花瓶不一定非得同“坚硬的容器”划等号——在下月开幕的米兰设计周上，日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\">nendo</a> 带来的 Jellyfish Vase 系列会让你重新思考花瓶的概念。这 30 只在水族箱中和花朵一起随水流漂浮的花瓶由超薄的透明硅胶制成，看起来相当轻盈的渐变蓝瓶身则是硅胶在经历两次染色加工后的成果，就像是一群大小不一的蓝色水母。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214237pZaUGdWzyiFSxgkC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214237BjHrgKQvfaUpuTcb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703222142379H1oBcga0lwpEfex.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703222142372FMuhcRK3peWz8sH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Brooch by Mikiji Nagai</h3><p>为了让服饰自带的 logo 变得更有趣，日本平面设计师<a href=\"http://www.mikiji.tv/\">永井ミキジ</a>推出了一套为它们加戏的胸针。四种胸针分别是看起来很适合 Lacoste 那枚鳄鱼 logo 的水族箱；比较百搭的 UFO 和老式电视机；借鉴兵库县议员野野村龙太郎在采访时爆哭一幕的讲台。这是它的<a href=\"http://kaijublue-shop.jp/products/list.php?mode=search&amp;category_id=&amp;name=%E3%83%AD%E3%82%B4%E3%81%A7%E3%81%82%E3%81%9D%E3%81%B6%E3%83%96%E3%83%AD%E3%83%BC%E3%83%81&amp;search.x=46&amp;search.y=19\">购买链接</a>，售价为 1080 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214255CuSRZTGklj0Jmg9e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644068\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214255UA5t8YRTkFPW64C9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214256px618kId9PrKoYaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612299\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hardlight VR Suit by NullSpace VR</h3><p>虽然现有的 VR 技术已经能够让玩家获得身临其境的游戏体验，但它们大多仅限于视觉上的反馈。为了弥补缺失的互动，来自美国的 VR 公司 NullSpace 研发了这款名为 Hardlight 的穿戴设备。它的外观和盔甲相似，内置的 16 个触觉反馈模块会根据玩家的动作产生不同程度的震动，模拟出实战的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/morgansinko/hardlight-vr-suit-dont-just-play-the-game-feel-it\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 499 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214313j7XqtvMRkmB0ChGD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214313KSG6m0EgBjJQ7wrH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.514706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703222143134Kaq6Uir2ekh9dWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.514706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214313GvsROVHq4QlAiP0x.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.866176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Konstella by Toyo Steel</h3><p>来自日本大阪的<a href=\"http://www.toyosteel.jp/\">东洋钢铁公司</a>此前一直以生产轻质钢铁制品为主业，去年它和产品研发工作室 <a href=\"http://www.iroyori.jp/\">Iroyori</a> 联手创立了以星座为名的包具品牌 <a href=\"http://konstella.jp/\">Konstella</a>。尽管造型上沿袭了传统的铁制工具盒，在橙色皮革的点缀下，三款包具并没有给人一种过于冰冷的感觉。不同于常见的皮革公文包，坚硬的表面可以在需要时变成一台工作桌面用于书写。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214619ED9shUip4L3kBwb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635671\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214619k8BYZb2i7uDn3Mmy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214619OVis93EDANSBMctu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596302\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214618gPJMSOL7vuiTNRdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Marchoc by Luminous Design Group</h3><p>有了好包装的加持，冲一杯拥有独特风味的巧克力也能被赋予独特的仪式感。最近，来自希腊 <a href=\"http://luminous.gr/\">Luminous Design Group</a> 的设计师就为饮料公司 <a href=\"http://www.gialousis.gr/\">Gialousis</a> 旗下的 Marchoc 巧克力粉设计了一套相当活泼的包装。对比鲜明的配色加上暗喻风味特征的插画，让罐头充满了艺术气息，即便空了也可以当作花器使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703222148094qbTnOxvtURPcd9W.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214809wJD9Y8ZrFUpRqs2G.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214809nVHNWrmy8o4PzGqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214809y4sx63QvL9adDOVb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214809wgYqr13jZIMlpyHW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Miniature Calendar by Tatsuya Tanaka</h3><p>假设这世界上真的有一个“小人国”，里面的生活会是什么样的呢？来自日本摄影师<a href=\"http://miniature-calendar.com/\">田中达也</a>的 Miniature Calendar 是一个始于 2011 年 4 月的摄影项目，在近六年的时间里，田中每天都会把迷你的人物模型和生活中常见的物品组合在一起，利用一大一小的反差模拟真实生活中的情境，有一种独特的幽默感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214718c3dpwv8qeFszOXx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214719ahBuC4LQT0XfnrU1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214719HbTy2onKUNh7t0gW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170322214719UvHn5SwL9j4PJ31Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>"}